<p>Your two geeks are joined by long-time Mac Geek Gab friend, Paul Kent, to talk all about the upcoming Macworld / iWorld 2014 show. Learn how the conference will focus on &ndash; and teach you about &ndash; the future of technology, iBeacons, Passbook, Bitcoins and, of course, all things Apple and Mac. Plus Dave and John go impromptu at the end to solve John&#39;s Google+ issues. All good, all free, all for you.</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
